object.extended: The DH system shall: Enable HK and science data flow – Housekeeping data (Temperatures, Pressures, Voltages, Currents, Status,...) – Attitude data – Payload data (e.g., Science data) - Receive and distribute commands - Perform TM and TC protocols - Distribute timing signals - Synchronization of data – Time stamping of data - Provide data storage - Execute commands and schedules - Control subsystems and payloads - Monitor spacecraft health - Make autonomous decisions - Perform data compression.
object.description: Command and Data Handling, it is the device that connects the other devices, it processes and deliver information.
